name: Google - DeviantArt Style
description:
I love both DeviantArt.com and Google, so I made a style for Google making Google looks like  DeviantArt. Now I have made the homepage and the searching result page of Google.I'll keep modifying some more pages of Google, which I visit daily.
If you like this style, keep following the update.
